  "title": "Contract Patient Service Associate Needed!! #HCGT",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>-         Providing frontline customer service and handling of any registrations, and appointments</p><p>-         Working closely with the practitioners and nurses to provide excellent patient care</p><p>-         Provide chaperone assistance to doctors/nurses</p><p>-         Attend to any requests, emails and phone enquiries</p><p>-         Collection of payments and basic admin duties</p><p>-         Ad-hoc duties</p><p>Job Requirements:</p><p>-         Minimum N/O/A Levels or Diploma in any studies are encouraged to apply</p><p>-         Able to commit a minimum of 3 months</p><p>-         Willing to walk and stand for long hours</p><p>-         Experience in customer service preferred but not a must as training will be provided</p><p>-         Office hours, 5.5 days</p><p>-         Able to start immediately/on short notice</p><p>All qualified applicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No.199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>",
